            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>D</abbr><ex>is</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>P</abbr><ex>atris</ex></expan> et <expan><ex>H</ex><abbr>ae</abbr><ex>re</ex><abbr>c</abbr></expan>(urae) <note>sic</note> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Caes</abbr><ex>ius</ex></expan> Iust<lb break="no" n="3"/>us et <expan><abbr>Fla</abbr><ex>vius</ex></expan> <lb n="4"/>Fronto <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>v</abbr><ex>otum</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>olverunt</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>l</abbr><ex>ibentes</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>m</abbr><ex>erito</ex></expan> <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>sac</abbr><ex>erdote</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> <expan><abbr>Fl</abbr><ex>avio</ex></expan> Salviano
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Z. 6 befindet sich auf der Crepido. Darunter eine sekundär angebrachte, moderne Inschrift &amp;quot;&amp;quot;A. Wosta&amp;quot;&amp;quot; oder &amp;quot;&amp;quot;A. Woska&amp;quot;&amp;quot;. Nach Kremer ist der Inschriftträger Altar oder Postament. Reste von roter Farbe in den Buchstaben. (B): CIL 03, 11087, Vorbeck: unterhalb von Z. 7: a suo sta(tuerunt).</p>
            </div>
